div.p: Total Loss = λ₁ × Box Loss + λ₂ × Objectness Loss + λ₃ × Classification Loss
λ values weight the importance of each component (e.g., λ_coord = 5, λ_noobj = 0.5 in YOLOv1)
Box Loss "How accurate are the coordinates?"
(x, y, w, h) MSE or IoU-based
Objectness Loss "Does this cell contain an object?"
Classification Loss "What class is this object?"
